---
By: Meher Baba
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 258
    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Hypocrisy
---
To have one eye glued on the enchanting pleasures of the flesh, and with
the other to expect to see a spark of Eternal Bliss, is not only impossible
but the height of hypocrisy.
